data.description: Stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a den and a 2-car garage, featuring an attractive green space in the front. Nestled in the desirable gated community of Andros Isle, this home boasts upgraded laminate flooring thru-out the living areas & bedrooms. The spacious kitchen showcases a modern stainless steel appliance package within the inviting eat-in area. Complete with elegant plantation shutters, this home presents itself impeccably, resembling a model home. Washer/Dryer will stay and were purchased in 2023. Wonderful gated community just minutes to downtown West Palm Beach, FL Turnpike, restaurants, beaches, and shopping. All ages welcome and pet friendly neighborhood!
